msgid "reminder_parse_error"
msgstr "I couldn't understand the time format. Please try again:\n\n`[Message] [day] [time]`\n\n*Examples:*\n• Take fishing rod tomorrow 16:00\n• Meeting mon 10:00\n• Meeting next thu 10:00\n• Coffee 14:30"

